cause.description:
During my trip to Hanover this past June it really opened my eyes to how much we take for granted in the United States. This cause is to support the churches and schools with the supplies that are needed. I will also be donating musical instruments.
1. Enhancing Hanover with the supplies that are needed.
cause.mission: Support the Hanover Province because of the limited resources.
cause.name: Project Hanover, Jamaica
